SQL DB

States: id, name

Cities: id, name, foreign key (state id)

Categories: id, name

Posting: id, foreign key (city id), foreign key (category id), posting title, price *, specific location *, postal code, posting body, make/manufacturer *, size/dimensions *, condition (dropdown *), email, users can also contact me by phone (checkbox *), users can also contact me by text (checkbox *) phone number *, extension *, contact name *, link to image1 *, link to image2 *, link to image3 *, link to image4 *

* designates optional field
